<h1>College Infrastructure</h1>
<table>
<tr>
<th colspan="2" class="center">Overview of the College</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" class="full-width">
<img src="./uvce.jpeg" alt="">
Our college is renowned for its excellent infrastructure, providing students with a conducive
environment for learning and growth. The campus is spread across a large area, featuring state-of-the-art
buildings, lush greenery, and a wide range of facilities to support both academic and extracurricular
activities.
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th>Library</th>
<th>Labs</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>
<p>The library is a hub of knowledge with over 50,000 books, journals, and digital resources.
Students have access to both quiet study zones and group discussion areas, providing an ideal space for all
kinds of academic work.</p>
<img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0347/6111/3736/products/NY-Public-Library-Main-Reading-Room.jpg?v=1593016850" alt="Library">
</td>
<td>
<p>Our labs are equipped with cutting-edge technology, providing hands-on experience in fields
like computer science, electronics, and engineering. Each lab is designed to foster innovation and critical
thinking.</p>
<img src="https://www.bnl.gov/today/body_pics/2012/02/d0880212-bldg480-hr.jpg" alt="Labs">
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th>Hostel</th>
<th>Sports Facilities</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>
<p>The college hostel offers a safe and comfortable living environment. With modern amenities
such as Wi-Fi, study rooms, and recreational spaces, it provides students with a home-like atmosphere away
from home.</p>
<img src="https://abrokenbackpack.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/czech-inn-1.jpg" alt="Hostel">
</td>
<td>
<p>Our college has world-class sports facilities, including football fields, basketball courts, and a
well-equipped gymnasium. Students are encouraged to engage in physical activities to maintain a healthy
balance between academics and sports.</p>
<img src="https://i.pinimg.com/originals/45/77/1d/45771d5271de091b31505609e776951b.jpg" alt="Sports Facilities">
</td>
